text: Troy Dale Jackson (born June 26, 1968) is an American politician. He is a member of the Maine Senate. In 2018, Jackson was elected President of the Maine Senate. On December 2, 2020, Jackson was re-elected to that position. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:21st-century American politicians Category:Living people Category:State legislators of the United States Category:Politicians from Maine Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
